## 2. 🎥 Reflection on Mock Interview Video Experience

### Situation
I had never recorded a formal mock interview before. The task required me to simulate a real job interview, present myself professionally on camera, and embed the video into my digital portfolio.

### Task
I needed to prepare for and record a mock interview, answer technical and behavioural questions related to networking, and then embed the video link into my portfolio using Markdown so that it was accessible to viewers.

### Action
I prepared by reviewing common Junior Network Engineer interview questions covering topics like VLANs and troubleshooting tools. I recorded the interview, uploaded it to YouTube, and embedded it into my portfolio using a Markdown badge-style link that directs viewers to the video.

### Result
The mock interview helped me identify gaps in how I communicate technical knowledge verbally. I became more confident articulating my project experience and connecting theory to practice. Embedding the video into my portfolio also taught me how to integrate multimedia content into a Markdown-based page, making the portfolio more engaging and professional.

